Make Goblins and Orcs quarrel
If the Goblin totem - the head of the First Goblin on a pole - is put on the Orcs' council mountain, the Orcs would be offended and attack the Goblins. And a quarrel between enemies could only help the village....
#subobj  1
Find the totem
The Goblins moved to the easternmost island and took the First Goblin's head with them.
#subobj  2
Take the totem
You must take the First Goblin's head from the Goblins.
#subobj  3
Toss the totem to the Orcs
The Orcs' council mountain is on the northern river bank. A path leads to the mountain top. Go along it to reach the summit and put the First Goblin's head up there.
